params.name: backbone_config
params.description: The configuration of the backbone in a dictionary or the config object of the backbone.

params.name: backbone
params.description: Name of backbone to use when backbone_config is None. If use_pretrained_backbone is True, thiswill load the corresponding pretrained weights from the timm or transformers library. If use_pretrained_backboneis False, this loads the backbones config and uses that to initialize the backbone with random weights.

params.name: use_pretrained_backbone
params.description: Whether to use pretrained weights for the backbone.

params.name: use_timm_backbone
params.description: Whether to load backbone from the timm library. If False, the backbone is loaded from the transformerslibrary.

params.name: backbone_kwargs
params.description: Keyword arguments to be passed to AutoBackbone when loading from a checkpointe.g. {out_indices: (0, 1, 2, 3)}. Cannot be specified if backbone_config is set.

params.name: hidden_size
params.description: Dimensionality of the encoder layers and the pooler layer.

params.name: num_hidden_layers
params.description: Number of hidden layers in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: num_attention_heads
params.description: Number of attention heads for each attention layer in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: intermediate_size
params.description: Dimensionality of the intermediate (i.e., feed-forward) layer in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: hidden_act
params.description: The non-linear activation function (function or string) in the encoder and pooler. If string, gelu,relu, selu and gelu_new are supported.

params.name: hidden_dropout_prob
params.description: The dropout probability for all fully connected layers in the embeddings, encoder, and pooler.

params.name: attention_probs_dropout_prob
params.description: The dropout ratio for the attention probabilities.

params.name: initializer_range
params.description: The standard deviation of the truncated_normal_initializer for initializing all weight matrices.

params.name: layer_norm_eps
params.description: The epsilon used by the layer normalization layers.

params.name: backbone_featmap_shape
params.description: Used only for the hybrid embedding type. The shape of the feature maps of the backbone.

params.name: qkv_bias
params.description: Whether to add a bias to the queries, keys and values.
